description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ("Spherophorus ridiculosus" (sic) Prevot 1948; Bacillus mortiferus; Bacillus necroticus; Bacteroides freundii; Clostridium rectum; Fusibacterium mortiferum; Fusubacterium ridiculosum; Hiblerillus rectus; Pseudobacterium freundii; Pseudobacterium mortiferum; Pseudobacterium necroticum; Spherophorus freundi; Spherophorus mortiferus; Spherophorus necroticus; Spherophorus ridiculosus.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
